    "message_type": "Markdown",
    "message": "<div style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 600px;'>\n\n<p>Dear {{ doc.prospect_name }},</p>\n\n<p>Thank you for reaching out to <strong>Pikt, Inc.</strong>! We've received your quote request and wanted to get you an instant estimate right away.</p>\n\n<div style='background: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #171717; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;'>\n  <h2 style='margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 18px;'>Your Estimated Monthly Investment</h2>\n  <p style='font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #171717; margin: 0;'>${{ '{:,.2f}'.format(doc.custom_estimate_low or 0) }} \u2013 ${{ '{:,.2f}'.format(doc.custom_estimate_high or 0) }}<span style='font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; color: #666;'>/month</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<p><strong>Based on your details:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Building Type:</strong> {{ doc.building_type }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Building Size:</strong> {{ doc.building_size }} sq ft</li>\n  <li><strong>Service Frequency:</strong> {{ doc.service_frequency }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Services Requested:</strong> {{ doc.service_interest or 'General Cleaning' }}</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>This is an <strong>instant estimate</strong> based on industry-standard rates. Your formal, itemized quote will be sent within <strong>24 hours</strong> and may vary slightly based on specific facility requirements.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What's included in our service:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>\u2705 Fully insured and bonded cleaning crew</li>\n  <li>\u2705 All cleaning supplies and equipment provided</li>\n  <li>\u2705 Consistent, scheduled service</li>\n  <li>\u2705 Online portal to manage your account</li>\n  <li>\u2705 24/7 support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you have any questions in the meantime, reply to this email or call us at <strong>512-994-6212</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>We look forward to working with you!</p>\n\n</div>",
